{"tid":1875821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有一位手足失蹤咗，麻煩大家幫手搵佢","createTime":"2020-02-12T04:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T08:31:27.000Z","uid":220066,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c601df32318ed1bd5e01eb43744ab63cdc1f057e","tid":1875821,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T04:23:57.000Z","msg":"佢就係一路默默支持手足的周國賢<br />\n一直以來無論社交平台同埋音樂作品<br />\n都係充滿著黃色意味<br />\n即使有好多藍絲係到攻擊腎仔<br />\n腎仔都反擊番對方轉頭<br />\n<br />\n由上年九月開始關閉Ig同其他社交平台<br />\n身為同路人嘅一班歌迷同手足唔希望佢有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係自問係佢粉絲好愛腎仔嘅話<br />\n希望大家可以將呢個post傳比佢身邊朋友<br />\n<br />\n希望可以得知腎仔最新情況<br />\n只求佢無事就足夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XVt86oJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXVt86oJ.png&h=7e91f33c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Lsvry_XKJRE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLsvry_XKJRE&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BYleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=75362697\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Lsvry_XKJRE</a>"},{"pid":"ea3ff9fb55cb1257a7cd3f4286abf3cc494d433f","tid":1875821,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T04:24:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bccf53432877d5778c9b6a06497d58ecb4637d1a","tid":1875821,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T04:25:10.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"4136276cee53cdbfade541eef735253f8d5ac5f6","tid":1875821,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T04:26:04.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"4d6cb82feddd630f722cf70a7581ec8eb273b770","tid":1875821,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T04:26:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8380aaa1534ea4cc570884e692963ac360d5b8b0","tid":1875821,"uid":113155,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-